<li><a href="https://github.com/driverdan/dropship">Dropship</a></li>
<li><a href="http://netzpolitik.org/2011/neues-feature-bei-dropbox-backdoor-fur-us-behorden/">Dropbox &amp; US-Behörden</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.adel.nursat.kz/apg/">AGP</a></li>
<li><a href="https://agilebits.com/onepassword">1Password</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.truecrypt.org/">TrueCrypt</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.wuala.com/de/">Wuala</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.aerofs.com/">AeroFS</a></li>
<li><a href="http://sparkleshare.org/">Sparkleshare</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.arg0.net/encfs">EncFS</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.boxcryptor.com/">Boxcryptor</a></li>
<li><a href="http://retroshare.sourceforge.net/">Retroshare</a></li>
<li><a href="https://pogoplug.com/">Pogoplug</a></li>
